{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-301-to-400/problem-350-constraining-the-least-greatest-and-the-greatest-least","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-301-to-400","demoType":null,"title":"Vežba 350: Sprečavanje malo više velikog i najveceg malo","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Orodha ya ukubwa $n$ ni mfululizo wa nambari asilia $n$. Mifano ni (2, 4, 6), (2, 6, 4), (10, 6, 15, 6), na (11).</p>\n<p>Najveći zajednički delilac, ili $gcd$, niza je najveći prirodan broj koji deli sve elemente tog niza. Primeri: $gcd(2, 6, 4) = 2$, $gcd(10, 6, 15, 6) = 1$ i $gcd(11) = 11$.</p>\n<p>Najmanji zajednički višekratnik, ili $lcm$, liste je najmanji prirodan broj koji deli svaki unos u listi. Primjeri: $lcm(2, 6, 4) = 12$, $lcm(10, 6, 15, 6) = 30$ i $lcm(11) = 11$.</p>\n<p>Izračunajte $f(G, L, N)$ kao broj nizova veličine $N$ koji imaju $gcd \\ge G$ i $lcm \\le L$. Primer:</p>\n<p>$$\\begin{align}\n&#x26; f(10, 100, 1) = 91 \\\\\n&#x26; f(10, 100, 2) = 327 \\\\\n&#x26; f(10, 100, 3) = 1135 \\\\\n&#x26; f(10, 100, 1000)\\bmod {101}^4 = 3\\,286\\,053\n\\end{align}$$</p>\n<p>Pronađi $f({10}^6, {10}^{12}, {10}^{18})\\bmod {101}^4$.</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f4cb1000cf542c50ffdd","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":302010,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-301-to-400/problem-350-constraining-the-least-greatest-and-the-greatest-least"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function leastGreatestAndGreatestLeast() {\n\n  return true;\n}\n\nleastGreatestAndGreatestLeast();","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissi